# Roadmap tracking

When starting implementation work on this project, read
`IMPLEMENTATION-ROADMAP.md` to identify the current phase and next pending task.

When a task's "Done" criterion is fully satisfied during a coding session:

1. Open `IMPLEMENTATION-ROADMAP.md`
2. Find the task by its ID (e.g. `1.1`, `2.5`, `3.8`)
3. Change `- [ ]` to `- [x]` for that task
4. If all tasks in a phase are complete, also mark the phase checkpoint items

Do not mark tasks that were only partially completed.
Do not mark tasks whose "Done" criterion has not been verified.
